Lin Zhang, Jianxin Wu, Yin Li. 2022. ActionFormer: Localizing Moments of Actions with Transformers . In European Conference on Computer Vision (ECCV), 492–510. https://doi.org/10.1007/978-3-031-19772-7_29 (36) Rui Zhang et al. 2023. Ummaformer: A Universal Multimodal-Adaptive Transformer Framework for Temporal Forgery Localization . https://doi.org/10.1145/3581783.3613767 (37) Christos Koutlis, Symeon Papadopoulos. 2024. DiModiF: Discourse Modality-Information Differentiation for Audio-Visual Deepfake Detection and Localization . https://doi.org/10.48550/arXiv.2411.10193 (38) Darius Afchar, Vincent Nozick, Junichi Yamagishi, Isao Echizen. 2018. Mesonet: a compact facial video forgery detection network . In 2018 IEEE International Workshop on Information Forensics and Security (WIFS), pages 1–7. IEEE. https://doi.org/10.1109/WIFS.2018.8630761 (39) Zhixi Cai, Shreya Ghosh, Abhinav Dhall, Tom Gedeon, Kalin Stefanov, Munawar Hayat. 2023. Glitch in the matrix: A large scale benchmark for content driven audio-visual forgery detection and localization . Computer Vision and Image Understanding, 236: 103818. https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cviu.2023.103818 (40) Dingfeng Shi, Yujie Zhong, Qiong Cao, Lin Ma, Jia Li, Dacheng Tao. 2023. Tridet: Temporal Action Detection with Relative Boundary Modeling . https://doi.org/10.1109/CVPR52729.2023.01808 (41) Y. Zhang et al. 2024. MFMS: Learning Modality-Fused and Modality-Specific Features for Deepfake Detection and Localization Tasks . https://doi.org/10.1145/3664647.3688984 (42) Ashish Vaswani et al. 2017. Attention Is All You Need . https://proceedings.neurips.cc/paper_files/paper/2017/file/3f5ee243547dee91fbd053c1c4a845aa-Paper.pdf (43) Weihao Yu et al. 2024. MetaFormer Baselines for Vision . IEEE Transactions on Pattern Analysis and Machine Intelligence. https://doi.org/10.1109/TPAMI.2023.3329173 (44) Zhaohui Zheng, Ping Wang, Wei Liu, Jinze Li, Rongguang Ye, Dongwei Ren. 2020. Distance-IoU Loss: Faster and Better Learning for Bounding